00:05:21.416 --> 00:05:23.539
You're building a giant ship in the middle of a desert.

00:05:24.821 --> 00:05:26.924
Well, the spiritual life is often like that, isn't it?

00:05:29.067 --> 00:05:29.708
What are you doing?

00:05:29.828 --> 00:05:30.509
What are you talking about?

00:05:30.709 --> 00:05:31.811
Why are you living this way?

00:05:31.831 --> 00:05:42.386
I think of many years ago when I first became a priest and you make this vow of celibacy and obedience and to live this religious life.

00:05:42.626 --> 00:05:46.891
You know, there are people then and now who would say, I don't get it.

00:05:46.931 --> 00:05:48.212
I mean, what are you doing?

00:05:48.833 --> 00:05:59.866
Well, the spiritual life's kind of like that because we're following this star, this indication, this hint that the longing will be fulfilled if we move in this direction.

00:05:59.986 --> 00:06:03.710
It's one of the dynamics of the spiritual life.

00:06:04.711 --> 00:06:05.813
Okay.

00:06:05.833 --> 00:06:10.578
So far, everything I've been talking about could be said really of anybody.

00:06:10.914 --> 00:06:12.957
of any spiritual seeker.

00:06:14.119 --> 00:06:22.211
Go into any bookstore and go into the spirituality section and you'll find books about the human aspiration for God, the longing for God.

00:06:22.531 --> 00:06:24.554
