00:06:24.674 --> 00:06:25.836
I'm not against that at all.

00:06:25.876 --> 00:06:26.777
I think that's beautiful.

00:06:26.818 --> 00:06:28.200
It's one of the great things about us.

00:06:29.181 --> 00:06:33.187
But now, now, here's the Christian difference.

00:06:34.749 --> 00:06:40.658
Christianity is not just one more account of how we're longing for

